With 2 events:
P(no events) = 1 - P(A ∪ B)
P(NOTA) = 1 - P(A)
P(NOTB) = 1 - P(B)
P(at least one event) = P(A ∪ B)
P(at least one event) = P(A) + P(B) - P(A ∩ B)
P(exactly one event) = P(A ∩ NOTB) + P(NOTA ∩ B)
P(exactly A) = P(A ∩ NOTB)
P(exactly B) = P(NOTA ∩ B)
P(exactly A and B) = P(A ∩ B)
P(at least two events) = P(A ∩ B)
P(A^C and B) = P(B) − P(A and B)
P(A and B^C) = P(A) - P(A and B)

With 3 events:
P(A ∩ B ∩ NOTC) = P(A ∩ B) − P(A ∩ B ∩ C)
P(A ∩ NOTB ∩ C) = P(A ∩ C) − P(A ∩ B ∩ C)
P(A ∪ B ∪ C) = P(A) + P(B) + P(C) - P(A ∩ B) - P(A ∩ C) - P(B ∩ C) + P(A∩B∩C)
P(no events) = 1 - P(A ∪ B ∪ C)
P(NOTA) = 1 - P(A)
P(NOTB) = 1 - P(B)
P(NOTC) = 1 - P(C)
P(at least one event) = P(A ∪ B ∪ C)
P(at least one event) = P(A) + P(B) + P(C) - P(A ∩ B) - P(A ∩ C) - P(B ∩ C) + P(A∩B∩C)
P(exactly one event) = P(A ∩ NOTB ∩ NOTC) + P(NOTA ∩ B ∩ NOTC) + P(NOTA ∩ NOTB ∩ C)
P(exactly A) = P(A ∩ NOTB ∩ NOTC)
P(exactly B) = P(NOTA ∩ B ∩ NOTC)
P(exactly C) = P(NOTA ∩ NOTB ∩ C)
P(exactly A and B) = P(A ∩ B ∩ NOTC)
P(exactly A and C) = P(A ∩ NOTB ∩ C)
P(exactly B and C) = P(NOTA ∩ B ∩ C)
P(exactly two events) = P(A∩ B ∩ NOTC) + P(A∩NOTB∩C) + P(NOTA ∩ B ∩ C)
P(At Most Two Events)=P(Exactly Zero Events)+P(Exactly One Event)+P(Exactly Two Events)
P(at least two events)=P(A∩B)+P(A∩C)+P(B∩C)−3×P(A∩B∩C)
P(at least two events) = P(exactly any two events) + P(A ∩ B ∩ C)
P(all three events) = P(A ∩ B ∩ C)
P(exactly three events) = P(A ∩ B ∩ C)
P(at least three events) = P(A ∩ B ∩ C)

two events:
P(M∣V)=  P(M∩V) / P(V)
P(V|M)=  P(V∩M) / P(M)
​P(M^C∣V) = 1−P(M∣V)
​P(V^C∣M) = 1−P(V∣M)

If event given event P(A∣B)= P(B|A)⋅P(A) / P(B)

ˉX = (x1 + x2 + x3 + xn) / n

sum of squares = (x1 - ˉX)^2 + (x2 - ˉX)^2 + (xn - ˉX)^2
sum of squared difference = (x1 - ˉX)^2 + (x2 - ˉX)^2 + (xn - ˉX)^2

variance of x = s^2 * x =  ˉx/ n -1
variance of y = s^2 * y = a^2 (s^2 x)
sY = sqrt( s^2 Y )

standard deviation = sqrt ( variance)

divation third observation = x_3 - ˉx
deviation first ovservation = x_1 - ˉx

ybar = a xbar + b
ybar = convertionfactor xbar + constant

Y_5 = a * x_5 + b

z-score fith transofmed = Y_5 - ybar / sY

mediam = middle
Q1 = median of lower half = 1+2 /2
Q2 = median
Q3 = median of upper half = 3+4 / 2
IQR=Q3−Q1

